    {"instruction": "Give me a budget version of Death and Taxes.", "input": "", "output": "D&T is already one of the more affordable Legacy decks since it is mostly mono-white. Skip the 1-2 Scrubland/Karakas splash (save $400-800). Run basic Plains instead. Replace Rishadan Port ($80 each) with additional Wastelands or Ghost Quarters if needed. The core of Thalia, Stoneforge Mystic, Aether Vial, Flickerwisp, and Swords to Plowshares is all affordable. Total budget build: $800-1200 vs $2500-3500 optimal."},
